the thrilling world of lacrosse like never before with LAXVR Skills, an unparalleled virtual reality experience. Crafted for both enthusiasts and novices, this game offers a chance to immerse yourself fully in the realm of lacrosse from a first-person perspective. Here's a glimpse into what awaits you:\n\n1. **Four Main Game Modes:** \n   **Shooting Mode:** Hone your shooting skills, master different techniques, and aim for that perfect shot.\n   **Goalie Mode:** Stand tall between the posts, anticipate your opponent's moves, and make that crucial save.\n   **Defender Mode:** Learn the art of defense, stop the attackers in their tracks, and reclaim the ball.\n   **The Medicine Game:** Embark on a historical journey that pays homage to the deep-rooted origins and traditions of lacrosse. Experience the soul of the game and its spiritual significance.\n\n2. **Casual Play Modes:** \n   **Wall Ball:** Perfect for those who cherish the simple joys of the game. Bounce, catch, and repeat. Sharpen your hand-eye coordination and reflexes.\n   **Free Shoot:** Sometimes, all you need is the open field, a stick, a goal, and a ball. Practice your shots or just enjoy the serenity of the virtual field.\n\n3. **Community and Competition:** \n   **Leaderboards:** Push your limits! Challenge yourself, compete with your friends, and see how you rank globally in the LAX VR community. ", "short_description": "Dive into LAXVR Skills and elevate your lacrosse game! Engage in thrilling drills: fire precision shots, stuff attackers, and de-twig attackers with decisive checks. Can you score a 2-pointer past our goalie? Stop a 12-yard step down shot? Or shut down an attacker's split dodge? Challenge awaits in every corner!"}]}, "developer_name": "Duper Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://laxvr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Duper Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.laxvr.com/", "category": null, "comfort_ra